
### Get admin profile
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Update admin profile
PATCH http://localhost:3000/admin/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Admin Smith",
  "email": "john.admin@example.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "department": "Information Technology",
  "title": "Chief Technology Officer"
}

### Update admin preferences
PATCH http://localhost:3000/admin/preferences
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weeklyReports": true,
  "systemAlerts": false,
  "theme": "dark",
  "timezone": "America/New_York"
}

### Change admin password
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/change-password
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "currentpassword123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword456"
}

### Get dashboard stats
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get recent activity
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard/activity
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get recent activity with limit
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard/activity?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get upcoming deadlines
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard/deadlines
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get upcoming deadlines with limit
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard/deadlines?limit=15
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get volunteers with goals count
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/volunteers-with-goals
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN